00:02:12,320 --> 00:02:15,119
and even tried to kill the messenger
seeking help at Telan Fortress.

24
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:17,199
The Divine Race isn't just our Senea Tribe.

25
00:02:17,800 --> 00:02:18,919
For example, the Tarta Tribe.

26
